OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782319683
OL,3,CMeet the teacher single-handedly
OL,4,Ctackling the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FA teacher who spends much of his time
OL,7,Ftouring schools in Surrey and Sussex
OL,8,Ftalking about how to combat the impact
OL,9,Fof the "Mansophere", says parents
OL,10,Fcontact him constantly worried about
OL,11,Fwhat their sons are looking at online.
OL,13,FMatt Pinkett describes himself as an
OL,14,Fexpert in masculinity - and he's
OL,15,Fdetermined to fight back against
OL,16,Fwhat's become known as "toxic
OL,17,Fmasculinity".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
