FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782319683
OL,3,CMeet the teacher single-handedly
OL,4,Ctackling the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FHe says the attitudes to women that
OL,7,Fboys encounter online are a huge worry
OL,8,Ffor parents with sons. "They don't
OL,9,Fknow how to talk to them about this
OL,10,Fstuff," he said. "So I am just trying
OL,11,Fto help out and giving them the tools
OL,12,Fthey need."
OL,14,FHe also spends much of his time in
OL,15,Fschools talking to teenagers and
OL,16,Festimates he has spoken to 10,000
OL,17,Fsecondary school pupils.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782319683
OL,3,CMeet the teacher single-handedly
OL,4,Ctackling the 'manosphere'
OL,6,F"It's important to put this message
OL,7,Finto schools because it is vulnerable
OL,8,Fboys who this stuff is being targeted
OL,9,Ftowards," said Matt.
OL,11,F"Many of them (young boys) are very
OL,12,Fmuch wanting to be a man, they can't
OL,13,Fwant to become a man and lots of the
OL,14,Fmanosphere and these toxic male
OL,15,Finfluencers, they know that.
OL,17,F"They're telling boys that there are
OL,18,Fways to be a man that sadly many boys
OL,19,Fdon't realise are harmful to women and
OL,20,Fto boys themselves."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782319683
OL,3,CMeet the teacher single-handedly
OL,4,Ctackling the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FInfluencers typically say that they
OL,7,Fare defending traditional male roles
OL,8,Fand values.
OL,10,FMatt has written three books on the
OL,11,Fsubject of boys, the most recent
OL,12,Fcalled Unmasking the Manosphere.
OL,14,FHis work continues as the government
OL,15,Fprepares to legislate to ban social
OL,16,Fmedia for all Under 16s.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782319683
OL,3,CMeet the teacher single-handedly
OL,4,Ctackling the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FWe joined Matt on a visit to speak to
OL,7,Fsixth form students at Seaford College
OL,8,Fin Sussex. Among the things he teaches
OL,9,Fpupils is a five point plan to help
OL,10,Fpeople safely intervene if they
OL,11,Fencounter misogynistic attitudes or
OL,12,Fbehaviour.
OL,14,FPupils here are respectful, thoughtful
OL,15,Fand considerate to others but mindful
OL,16,Fof how they might be targeted online
OL,17,Fand how widespread the risks are.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782319683
OL,3,CMeet the teacher single-handedly
OL,4,Ctackling the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FXander, age 17, said: "I like to watch
OL,7,Fsport clips but every few scrolls I'd
OL,8,Fsay there will be a term about
OL,9,Fmisogyny. There will be a small clip
OL,10,Fof a streamer or a Youtuber
OL,11,Fdisrespecting a woman in a way that's
OL,12,Fglossed over. But it's not just a
OL,13,Fcasual joke throw, that small video
OL,14,Fgoes out to millions."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782319683
OL,3,CMeet the teacher single-handedly
OL,4,Ctackling the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FEva, age 17, said: "It's become
OL,7,Fextremely normalised, it will be fed
OL,8,Finto our algorithms, whether that's on
OL,9,FTik Tok or in the comments. And I
OL,10,Fthink bringing those into schools and
OL,11,Fhearing what toxic masculinity really
OL,12,Fis just makes us all so much more
OL,13,Faware."
OL,15,FNationally, the wider backdrop to all
OL,16,Fthis is shocking. Sixty-four per cent
OL,17,Fof teachers say they hear sexist
OL,18,Flanguage at least every week.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782319683
OL,3,CMeet the teacher single-handedly
OL,4,Ctackling the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FAnd more than a third of girls in
OL,7,Fmixed sex secondary schools say
OL,8,Fthey've experienced sexual harassment.
OL,10,FA lot of Matt's sessions are spent
OL,11,Fgiving pupils tips and hints on ways
OL,12,Fthat kind of behaviour can be combated
OL,13,Fand called out by others.
OL,15,FSonny, aged 16, said: "It's eye-
OL,16,Fopening hearing what Matt has to say
OL,17,Fand you just realise how much you hear
OL,18,Fand absorb without necessarily
OL,19,Frealising it."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782319683
OL,3,CMeet the teacher single-handedly
OL,4,Ctackling the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FSeventeen-year-old Annabel said: "I
OL,7,Fwill take away the positives, the
OL,8,Fpeople who are trying to change the
OL,9,Fnarrative around this toxic
OL,10,Fmasculinity, the whole manosphere."
OL,12,FMatt, who sometimes wears a beanie
OL,13,Fduring his talks, says: "I do think
OL,14,Fit's important for lads to see a
OL,15,Fblokey geezerish type of person
OL,16,Fadvocating for women and good things.
OL,17,FI am not unaware of the fact that how
OL,18,FI present myself plays a part in boys'
OL,19,Fwillingness to listen."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782319683
OL,3,CMeet the teacher single-handedly
OL,4,Ctackling the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FSeaford College says its pupils are
OL,7,Fall taught to be respectful and to
OL,8,Fmanage the risks of online content.
OL,9,FThey say inviting someone like Matt
OL,10,Finto school means they are helping to
OL,11,Fequip young people for now and what's
OL,12,Fto come.
OL,14,FDirector and Head of Sixth Form, James
OL,15,FKimber, said: "These lessons about
OL,16,Fmisogyny and the mansophere are things
OL,17,Fthat they are going to be able to take
OL,18,Fwith them into the future.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782319683
OL,3,CMeet the teacher single-handedly
OL,4,Ctackling the 'manosphere'
OL,6,F"These things aren't just appearing in
OL,7,Fschools, they are things they are
OL,8,Fgoing to experience in the workplace
OL,9,Fand we want to give them the tools to
OL,10,Ffuture proof themselves, to go out
OL,11,Finto the wider world. "
OL,13,FAssistant headteacher, Jo Forman, who
OL,14,Fis responsible for safeguarding and
OL,15,Fwellbeing, said: "We've never really
OL,16,Fshied away from complex topics, the
OL,17,Fminute you shy away from them they
OL,18,Fbecome bigger.
OL,20,F"I think it's a difficult conversation
OL,21,Fbut we have to have it."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
