PN,38712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1782319683
OL,3,CMeet the teacher single-handedly
OL,4,Ctackling the 'manosphere'
OL,6,FThe government is currently
OL,7,Fconsidering new measures to protect
OL,8,Fchildren online and says it wants to
OL,9,Fsee a ban on social media for all
OL,10,FUnder 16s next year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/12
